author: J-W Staff Reports
title: Game balls and gassers: KU vs. Texas Tech
text:
Advertisement Game Balls 
Linebacker Joe Dineen, aka Local Boy, was all over the field delivering hits and fished with 10 tackles, 2.5 for a loss. 
Defensive tackle Daniel Wise had a sack, a pass break-up, a quarterback hurry, a blocked extra point and five tackles. Gassers 
The kickers. Nick Bartolotta missed a 22-yard field goal and Matthew Wyman, suddenly the team’s best punter, missed an extra point and two field goals. 
Right guard Jacob Bragg was flagged for two false-start penalties in the first quarter.
